Sentencas: An unconventional high temperature fuel cell system, the liquid tin anode solid oxide fuel cell (LTA-SOFC), is discussed.
Titulo: Basic properties of a liquid tin anode solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A thermodynamic analysis of a solid oxide fuel cell with a liquid metal anode is developed.
Titulo: Basic properties of a liquid tin anode solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Pertinent thermochemical and thermophysical properties of liquid tin in particular are detailed.
Titulo: Basic properties of a liquid tin anode solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: An experimental setup for analysis of LTA-SOFC anode kinetics is described, and data for a planar cell under hydrogen indicated an effective oxygen diffusion coefficient of 5.3 x 10(-5) cm(2) s(-1) at 800 degrees C and 8.9 x 10(-5) cm(2) s(-1) 900 degrees C.
Titulo: Basic properties of a liquid tin anode solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This value is similar to previously reported literature values for liquid tin.
Titulo: Basic properties of a liquid tin anode solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The oxygen conductivity through the tin, calculated from measured diffusion coefficients and theoretical oxygen solubility limits, is found to be on the same order of that of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ), a traditional SOFC electrolyte material.
Titulo: Basic properties of a liquid tin anode solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: As such, the ohmic loss due to oxygen transport through the tin layer must be considered in practical system cell design since the tin layer will usually be at least as thick as the electrolyte.
Titulo: Basic properties of a liquid tin anode solid oxide fuel cell
